1. (n*(n+1)*(2*n+1))/6 = 1^2+2^2+3^2+.....+n^2
2. n*(n+1)/2 = 1+2+3+...+n
3. (n*(n+1)/2)^2 = 1^3+2^3+3^3+......+n^3
4. a/(1-r) sum of infinite geometrical progression
5. a(1-r^n)/(1-r) sum of finite geometrical progression
6. n/2*(a+(n-1)*d) sum of linear progression
7. a+(n-1)*d n'th element of a linear progression
8.(1*1!)+(2*2!)+(3*3!)+……+(n*n!)=(n+1)!-1
